The chips were good but the salsa sucked....tasted like pizza sauce, I mean really how hard is good salsa...
I ordered.....carne asada.... ....a staple in the catalog of good Mexican fair....but  NO...it was horrible (believe it or not, I'm being kind here!
)  It was a cut of meat that I'd never seen served in this capacity.......not sure what the h&ll it was...only thing I know for sure, it was bad....over cooked, and chewy...how does that happen?
